data.description: Welcome to this meticulously renovated hi-ranch in West Hempstead with Malverne schools. Situated on a large corner lot with plenty of backyard space, you can move right in and start enjoying life. Upon entering, you'll find an open concept living, dining room, and kitchen along with a full bathroom and three bedrooms. Gorgeous hardwood floors throughout the top floor. There is a full finished ground floor with a large 4th bedroom, bathroom, 2nd living room, laundry room and renovated garage.  All the upgrades have been done for you: brand new roof, brand new central AC, custom closet in primary bedroom, sprinkler system, a water filtration system throughout the entire house, smart features throughout the house including alarm system, ring cameras, and Nest thermostats. Enjoy the warm weather in your oversized backyard with a brand new patio and manicured lawn. Close to transportation and highways. Welcome Home!
